description:
Protect your canoe and car during transit with these handy foam blocks.

  • Made of high-density closed-cell foam
  • Grooves in the base for grip
  • Trapezoidal shape, with a groove in the top to fit your boat
  • 2 or more blocks may be required for safe transport. Blocks are sold individually
  • Dimensions are 9.5 x 10 x 16.5cm
name: Level Six Canoe Foam Block
